<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Evently - Registration Success</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        font-family: "Poppins", Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px 0;
        width: 100% !important;
        -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
        -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      /* Header */
      .header {
        background: #4caf50;
        color: white;
        padding: 32px 24px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #ffffff; /* Pastikan warna teks tetap putih */
      }

      /* Content */
      .content {
        padding: 32px 24px;
      }

      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #374151;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .info-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 20px 0 32px 0;
        background: #f9fafb;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .info-list li {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .info-list li:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }

      .info-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #374151;
      }

      .info-value {
        color: #6b7280;
      }

      /* Button */
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #4caf50;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 28px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 15px;
        transition: background 0.2s ease;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background: #388e3c;
      }

      /* Footer */
      .footer {
        background: #f9fafb;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #9ca3af;
        padding: 16px;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      }

      /* Responsiveness (tetap berguna untuk beberapa client) */
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .container-wrapper {
          padding: 10px !important;
        }

        .container {
          width: 100% !important;
        }

        .header,
        .content {
          padding: 24px 16px !important;
        }

        .info-list li {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 4px;
        }

        .button {
          width: calc(100% - 56px); /* Kalkulasi width agar padding tidak merusak layout */
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f5f7fa">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" class="container-wrapper" style="padding: 20px">
          <table
            class="container"
            width="600"
            border="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            align="center"
            style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); overflow: hidden"
          >
            <tr>
              <td class="header" style="background: #4caf50; color: white; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center">
                <h1 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #ffffff; margin: 0">Evently</h1>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="content" style="padding: 32px 24px">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px">Halo <%= username %>,</p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px">Terima kasih telah mendaftar di Evently. Berikut adalah informasi akun Anda:</p>

                <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0 32px 0">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151">Nama</td>
                    <td align="right" style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280"><%= username %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151">Email</td>
                    <td align="right" style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280"><%= email %></td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 12px 0; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151">Tanggal Registrasi</td>
                    <td align="right" style="padding: 12px 0; font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280">
                      <%= new Date(createdAt).toLocaleDateString("id-ID", { day:"2-digit", month:"long", year:"numeric" }) %>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px">Untuk memulai penggunaan Evently, silakan klik tombol berikut untuk verifikasi akun Anda.</p>

                <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Aktifkan Akun</a>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px">Jika Anda memiliki pertanyaan atau masalah, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.</p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #374151; font-size: 15px">Terima kasih telah bergabung dengan Evently!</p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td class="footer" style="background: #f9fafb; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; padding: 16px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb">
                <p style="margin: 0">&copy; 2025 Evently. All rights reserved.</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
